      "content": "wait really?? i've heard from a few people in my study group that it's fine as long as you don't take too much of the supplement. they said it just helps the sertraline work better and it's not like taking extra meds or anything since it's just a plant. are you sure it's actually that dangerous? i'm just really struggling to focus right now.",
